Reasoning: The paper deals with image analysis pipelines and the use of prior knowledge to improve their result quality. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of fuzzy set theory and the focus on improving performance also suggest a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the mention of terabyte-scale microscopy data and the need for efficient algorithms suggest a connection to neural networks (cs.NE).
